description:
&lt;p&gt;The Trust is seeking to appoint a highly motivated and enthusiastic individual to the role of Assistant Management Accountant within the Financial Management team. The role will provide the necessary support to the Senior Management Accountant and Finance Assistant to ensure the provision of a high quality financial advice and support service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Key responsibilities include review of the centre&#39;s month end position to identify variances ,complex transaction processing tasks and budget holder meetings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate must possess good organisational, time management and communication skills, as well as being proficient in the use of Microsoft Office, particularly Microsoft Excel.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please refer to the job description and person specification to ensure that you have the necessary skills and experience to apply for the post.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note this post will close at sufficient applicants&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameJudith WheadonJob titleSenior Management AccountantEmail addressjudith.wheadon@nhs.netTelephone number01642 835627&lt;/p&gt;
